{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/how-to-detect-the-theme-and-apps-from-any-shopify-store","result":{"pageContext":{"id":2061,"date":"2022-12-06T23:03:45","date_gmt":"2022-12-06T23:03:45","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=2061"},"modified":"2022-12-06T23:25:50","modified_gmt":"2022-12-06T23:25:50","slug":"how-to-detect-the-theme-and-apps-from-any-shopify-store","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/how-to-detect-the-theme-and-apps-from-any-shopify-store/","title":{"rendered":"How to detect the theme and apps from any Shopify store"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Have you ever found a Shopify store that caught your attention and wondered what theme it was built in so you could use it yourself? Or found an interesting app providing functionality that you didn&#8217;t knew how to acquire? <br><br>While Shopify itself offers no real way for you to obtain such information, our <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/shopify-app-detector-by-e/fhkelfkhcaokghlkckfgjoejhanelped?hl=en&amp;authuser=1\">Shopify App Detector by EZFY</a> can do just that. Just install it on chrome and we&#8217;ll teach you how to use it below.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-how-to-use-the-extension\">How to use the extension</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>First thing first, you&#8217;ll have to install the extension as mentioned above. You can find it <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/shopify-app-detector-by-e/fhkelfkhcaokghlkckfgjoejhanelped?hl=en&amp;authuser=1\">here</a> and remember it only works on Google chrome.<br></li><li>Click on the puzzle piece shaped &#8220;Extensions&#8221; icon at the top right of the Chrome screen. In the popup that opens, click on the pin icon to the right of the &#8220;Shopify App Detector by EZFY&#8221;. You only need to do this once to stick the extension to the bar, and if you want to hide the extension again just repeat the process.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1289\" height=\"643\" class=\"wp-image-2110\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Screenshot_5.png\" alt=\"Activating the Shopify Add Detector extension on the gfuel store\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Screenshot_5.png 1289w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Screenshot_5-850x424.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Screenshot_5-1200x599.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Screenshot_5-768x383.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1289px) 100vw, 1289px\" /><br></li><li>While in a site that was created using Shopify, make sure the page is fully loaded and just click the extension icon near the puzzle piece icon. This will open another popup window with all the information you&#8217;re looking for!<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"944\" height=\"746\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2116\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-5.png 944w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-5-850x672.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-5-768x607.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 944px) 100vw, 944px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that the extension has been installed and setup, you can use it on any Shopify store where you want to find the theme and apps being used, giving you much needed information in case you want to employ them in your own store.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Continue reading</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps\">&#8211; How to make slideshow images stop cutting off</a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps\">&#8211; Disable right click, image and text copying and improve your store&#8217;s security</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to use the Shopify App Detector by EZFY extension, which will inform you the theme and all apps used by any Shopify store you visit.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2122,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[206],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/publisher-zoom-2-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/publisher-zoom-2-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/publisher-zoom-2-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["all themes"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/publisher-zoom-2.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/2061"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=2061"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/2061/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2119,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/2061/revisions/2119"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/2122"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=2061"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=2061"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=2061"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes